author: Allum Bokhari
title: Facebook Coronavirus ‘Fact Checker’ Worked with Wuhan Virus Lab
description: Facebook is relying on a "fact checker" that uses "expert opinion" from a researcher who conducted projects with the Wuhan Institute of Virology, the biolab next to the wet market in the Chinese city of Wuhan where the Chinese virus originated.
